Keep exp to 60 seconds or less. Use jti for replay detection if the tool is high-risk.

### 6.3 Key management

Store the signing **private key** in Google-side secrets, not in git. App Hosting integrates with Cloud Secret Manager, and Cloudflare provides secrets bindings for the tool side. Publish the corresponding **public key** from the master app as a JWKS document at /.well-known/jwks.json so every tool can verify launch tokens without sharing the private key.

